            <section id="overview" class="card">
                <h2>🛡️ HIPAA Compliance Overview</h2>
                
                <div class="alert alert-danger">
                    <h4>🚨 HIPAA Requirements for Employee Data with Active-Active DR</h4>
                    <p>The Employee Onboarding Platform handles sensitive employee information that may include Protected Health Information (PHI) and Personally Identifiable Information (PII). Our implementation ensures full HIPAA compliance with comprehensive security measures, active-active EKS RTF cluster deployment, automated disaster recovery, and complete incident response procedures.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="component-grid">
                    <div class="nav-card">
                        <div class="nav-card-icon">🔐</div>
                        <h3>AES-256 Encryption</h3>
                        <p>Data encrypted at rest and in transit with military-grade security across all regions</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="nav-card">
                        <div class="nav-card-icon">🏗️</div>
                        <h3>Active-Active EKS RTF</h3>
                        <p>Zero-downtime architecture with automatic failover and load balancing</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="nav-card">
                        <div class="nav-card-icon">🔄</div>
                        <h3>99.99% Uptime</h3>
                        <p>Automated disaster recovery with < 30s RTO and < 5min RPO</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="nav-card">
                        <div class="nav-card-icon">📋</div>
                        <h3>Complete Audit Trail</h3>
                        <p>Every data access and modification logged across all regions</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

