                    <p>Comprehensive healthcare data protection with enterprise-grade security and disaster recovery capabilities.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="footer-section">
                    <h4>📞 Support Contacts</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Security Team: security@company.com</li>
                        <li>Compliance Officer: compliance@company.com</li>
                        <li>Emergency Hotline: +1-800-SECURITY</li>
                        <li>24/7 SOC: soc@company.com</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="footer-section">
                    <h4>🔗 Quick Links</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li><a href="#overview">HIPAA Overview</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#active-eks-architecture">EKS Architecture</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#dr-strategy">DR Strategy</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#compliance-checklist">Compliance Checklist</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="footer-section">
                    <h4>📊 System Status</h4>
                    <div class="status-indicator">
                        <span class="status-dot status-operational"></span>
                        <span>All Systems Operational</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="status-indicator">
                        <span class="status-dot status-operational"></span>
                        <span>HIPAA Compliance: 98.5%</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="status-indicator">
                        <span class="status-dot status-operational"></span>
                        <span>DR Ready: Active</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="footer-bottom">
                <p>&copy; 2026 Employee Onboarding Platform. All rights reserved. | 
                   <a href="#privacy">Privacy Policy</a> | 
